D.q[5464] = "Ah, yoo not know cousin mee? Hee Ronan the Barbarian. Hee walk near Brakmar.";
D.q[4439] = "How dare you quit!? I should have you chinese drip tortured until your head looks like a doughnut, but all the same, I like your courage. You do your own thing, and you don\'t mind showing it. I\'m going to forget about this littl incident, but don\'t let it happen again.";
